SELECT
  f.folder_name,
  p.project_name,
  p.project_id,
  CONCAT(CODE_POINTS_TO_STRING([127812 + MOD(ABS(FARM_FINGERPRINT(p.project_name)), 50)]), ' ', p.project_name) AS project_name_formatted,
  COUNT(t.task_id) AS total_loops
FROM `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.fct_tasks_v3` t
JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_projects_v3` p
  ON t.project_id = p.project_id
JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_folders_v3` f
  ON f.folder_id = p.group_id
WHERE t.status = 0
  AND COALESCE(p.closed, FALSE) = FALSE
  AND t.kind = 'TASK'
  AND f.folder_name NOT IN ('ðŸ’¤on hold lists', 'ðŸš€SOMEDAY lists', 'ðŸ›©ï¸Horizon of focus')
  AND p.project_name != 'ðŸ“ref - tickler notes for the day'
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4
ORDER BY 1 ASC, 5 DESC
LIMIT 500

SELECT
  f.folder_name,
  p.project_name,
  p.project_id,
  COUNT(t.task_id) AS tasks
FROM `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_projects_v3` p
JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_folders_v3` f
  ON f.folder_id = p.group_id
LEFT JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.fct_tasks_v3` t
  ON t.project_id = p.project_id
WHERE COALESCE(p.closed, FALSE) = FALSE
  AND f.folder_name NOT IN ('ðŸš€SOMEDAY lists', 'ðŸ›©ï¸Horizon of focus', 'default', 'ðŸ’¤on hold lists')
GROUP BY 1,2,3
HAVING COUNT(t.task_id) = 0
ORDER BY 1 ASC, 4 ASC
LIMIT 500

SELECT
  f.folder_name,
  p.project_name,
  p.project_id,
  p.last_pulse,
  DATE_DIFF(CURRENT_DATE(), DATE(p.last_pulse), DAY) AS days_last_active,
  COUNTIF(t.status = 0 AND t.kind = 'TASK') AS open_tasks
FROM `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_projects_v3` p
JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.dim_folders_v3` f
  ON f.folder_id = p.group_id
LEFT JOIN `airbyte-468412.ticktick_dbt_dev.fct_tasks_v3` t
  ON t.project_id = p.project_id
WHERE COALESCE(p.closed, FALSE) = FALSE
  AND f.folder_name NOT IN ('ðŸš€SOMEDAY lists', 'ðŸ›©ï¸Horizon of focus', 'default', 'ðŸ’¤on hold lists')
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4
HAVING DATE_DIFF(CURRENT_DATE(), DATE(p.last_pulse), DAY) > 5
ORDER BY days_last_active DESC, f.folder_name ASC, open_tasks ASC
LIMIT 500
